The paper proposes a new consensus mechanism for blockchains that utilizes the computation power of miners for deep learning training. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of cryptography (cs.CR), distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), machine learning (cs.LG), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
